  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张图来梳理几种博弈类型之间的关系。核心想法是从Risk出发，经过Signal传导，最终影响到Bargaining。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Risk到Signal是一条链。那Bargaining这边，我注意到它应该和Bailout形成双向关系，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Bargaining和Bailout是互相影响的。另外Compliance和Coding这两个节点，都要汇聚到Definition。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Compliance指向Definition，Coding也指向Definition。现在Definition还要连到Bargaining吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Definition会驱动Bargaining。还有Place这个节点，它跟Press的关系是独立的，你单独放出来就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Place到Press已经加上了。我检查一下流向：Risk→Signal→Barg，同时Bail↔Barg双向，这个结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等一下，Signal到Bargaining的箭头方向我刚才说反了。应该是Signal指向Barg，不是反过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，Signal→Barg。现在所有节点：Compliance game、Bailout game、Bargaining game、Coding game、Definition game，还有Risk、Signal、Place、Press。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "节点名称用英文game后缀统一，但显示标签要完整。Bailout到Bargaining的双向箭头别忘了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "双向箭头已确认。再核对一遍：Audit→Define，Code→Define，Define→Barg，Bail↔Barg，Risk→Signal→Barg，Place→Press。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "布局用LR横向吧，从左到右体现从Risk到Bargaining的传导逻辑，Compliance和Coding从上方汇入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Barg",
        "Audit",
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "横向布局已设置。所有关系都连上了，Bargaining处于中心位置，接收Signal、Definition和Bailout的输入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Signal",
        "Define",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了。这张图清晰展示了从风险信号到博弈决策，再到合规与编码定义的完整链条。",
      "elements_involved": [
